---
title: Hoisin Honey Chicken with Green Beans & Jasmine Rice
description: Tonight’s chicken dish is sweet, savory and spicy thanks to a combo of honey, hoisin, Sriracha, and fresh ginger. On the side, there’s crisp green beans and a heap of steamy rice. Oh, and did we mention it only takes 20 minutes to whip this up in your own kitchen? Winner winner chicken dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/61f98807dc87845a6a01df6c-8ed7a826.jpg
